{"tid":1956148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日網民創新口號避免集近閉呼籲積極防疫 集近閉讀音與習近平一樣","createTime":"2020-04-03T03:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T04:49:23.000Z","uid":290118,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68d12db16912c8dded6a371c1c052b75670624e7","tid":1956148,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"日本政府以「避免三密」來呼籲國民積極防疫：避免過密（人多的地方）、密切（密切接觸）、密閉（密封空間）。不過，「三密」較難懂，不太受歡迎。於是，網民就發明了新的口號「避免集近閉」：避免聚集、接近、密閉。「集近閉（しゅうきんぺい=SHU KIN PEI）」的日文讀法跟中國國家主席的姓名一樣，他都按日文讀法就念成SHU KIN PEI，因此網民讚這個更容易記住。<br />\n<br />\nネット民「やってはいけない事は&ldquo;シューキンペイ&rdquo;と覚えよう 『集、多数が集まるのは危険』『近、近くで話したり歌うのは危険』『閉、閉鎖された換気の悪い場所は危険』〜ネットの反応「これは覚えやすいw」「集近閉いいねｗ 三密よりわかりやすい」<br />\n<a href=\"https://anonymous-post.mobi/archives/22209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanonymous-post.mobi%2Farchives%2F22209&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BiBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=ed9dd425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://anonymous-post.mobi/archives/22209</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nipponsokuho/posts/2832674043482507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnipponsokuho%2Fposts%2F2832674043482507&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BiBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=13a6639c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nipponsokuho/posts/2832674043482507</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/03/AqWbSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F03%2FAqWbSZ.png&h=7603afff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/03/Bv9lgh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F03%2FBv9lgh.jpg&h=6a926af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ded8a956896736a9d86866a29dfd69193ac999c2","tid":1956148,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"習失腳<br />\n習敗北<br />\n甴近平<br />\n甴曱平<br />\n甴近病<